 ﾟﾟﾟ  ｰ ﾛ The Skid Rowdies are looking new blood to fill up the ranks.   ﾛ ﾛ
      ｱ ﾛ We're a professional team of dedicated sceners with big mark   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ under sceners. We believe on the ground idealism of the root   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ of the real old school scene. We do all this for fun and       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ nothing else. We don't earn anything on our hobby as we do     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ this for the competition and the heart of what got the scene   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ started in the mid eighties.                                   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ If you think you got something to offer, then don't hold back  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ on contacting us as soon as possible.                          ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Skid Row 2009                                                  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ On with the update release information:                        ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Version 1.06                                                   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Features:                                                      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Ship starting spots have been changed in battles. Ships now  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ   start further apart.                                         ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - The winners of the Commander competition have been added to  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ   commander faces                                              ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Check for update now informs if a patch is not available     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Ship movement has been improved                              ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Ships now always surrender with zero morale                  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Ship masts will fall only when mast hitpoints go under 10 %  ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Crew morale will go down when masts fall                     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Ships with masts down won't try to flee anymore              ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Cannons will get destroyed more easily                       ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ Bug Fixes:                                                     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Problems with some graphics cards fixed                      ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Problem with special characters in Windows User Name fixed   ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ - Problem with game sometimes freezing in battle end fixed     ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ﾛ                                                                ﾛ ﾛ
      ﾛ ｰ                                                                ﾛ ｰ
